1
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,440
Princess. Aya.

2
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,600
Who are you?

3
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,340
I'm the Prince.

4
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,690
Have you forgotten?

5
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,660
My looks haven't changed,

6
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,960
have they?

7
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,000
Could he have taken Buluotuo's Tears

8
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,120
for himself

9
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,800
and gained immortality?

10
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,160
Let's go.

11
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,520
We found the second Copper Frog.

12
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,720
Time to find the third.

13
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,040
You are looking for Copper Frogs too?

14
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:27,640
Of course.

15
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,240
Without finding the Copper Frogs,

16
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,440
how can I restore the Princess's memory

17
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,970
and find Buluotuo's Tears?

18
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,560
Aya.

19
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,570
Don't trust him.

20
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,920
His background is unknown.

21
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,200
He's clearly up to no good.

22
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:35,600
You...

23
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,690
Come with me.

24
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,490
It's dangerous.

25
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,880
Where are you going?

26
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,530
Who exactly are you people?

27
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,880
He lured Aya away.

28
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:53,560
I was actually going to ask you.

29
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,240
Your people

30
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,600
took the Copper Frog.

31
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,280
You're still talking?

32
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,930
They're already long gone.

33
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,520
What's wrong?

34
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,480
What is this?

35
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:26,120
Her side effects from entering the system

36
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,520
are even worse than mine.

37
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:32,120
This is a carriage from the future.

38
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,920
It can travel a thousand miles a day,

39
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,360
and eight hundred at night.

40
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,680
Such a divine object,

41
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,520
yet there are so many of them.

42
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,720
This is called the Iron-Armored Rhinoceros.

43
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,250
Everyone has one nowadays.

44
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,520
Excellent.

45
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,480
I'm talking nonsense here,

46
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,120
yet she managed not to laugh.

47
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,520
Is she testing me?

48
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,280
Her acting is so good.

49
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,400
Even I was fooled.

50
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,900
Where are we going?

51
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,980
The Great Rift Valley.

52
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,160
The next bronze frog

53
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,020
is right there.

54
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,650
Shine the light.

55
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,440
This is

56
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,490
a bronze mirror.

57
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,560
What bronze mirror?

58
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,640
It's just an ordinary mirror.

59
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,570
A makeup mirror.

60
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,970
Listen to music.

61
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,360
What is this magical object?

62
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:52,720
It's a music app.

63
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,659
It plays songs.

64
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,320
What?

65
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,250
Sounds good, right?

66
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,400
After we escaped from the Sinkhole,

67
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,600
we headed straight for Siam.

68
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:14,040
Even though we traveled by night and hid by day,

69
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,040
Marquis Hu still tracked us down.

70
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,360
Just as we were about to leave the Great Ming border,

71
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,560
Marquis Hu kidnapped the Prince and me.

72
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,000
But when we were at the Tiankeng,

73
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,800
didn't Huhou want to kill you...

74
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:46,880
and us?

75
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,000
Then why didn't he make a move?

76
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,130
Have you forgotten?

77
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,520
He used Buluotuo's Tear

78
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,320
to tempt you back then.
